{"tid":687236,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"道具鈔票裁決被斥為國際笑話　湯家驊指說法誇張　批評「自己做的事大晒」文化","createTime":"2018-06-02T05:21:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-02T05:47:50.000Z","uid":1221,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"396776478a10106e2e03348c0df78bbf654e9be5","tid":687236,"uid":1221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T05:21:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180601/s00001/3a320a1a919143a7206049c9de7449d9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180601%2Fs00001%2F3a320a1a919143a7206049c9de7449d9.jpg&h=791e4e4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n電影道具領班在借出道具鈔票後，與借用者同被控管有逾22萬張印有「道具」字眼的仿製紙幣，經審訊後被裁定保管偽製紙幣罪罪成，判囚4個月、緩刑2年。香港電影工作者總會昨指裁決淪為國際電影業界笑話。資深大律師兼行會成員湯家驊今在港台節目指出，有關說法「誇張」，目前香港出現一種文化，「自己做嘅嘢最大晒、最重要、最有凌駕性」、「法律都要靠邊站」，卻不顧社會責任和整體利益。<br />\n<br />\n湯家驊指出，針對仿製鈔票的相關法例已存在多年，「點解電影從業員會唔知呢？全行都唔知喎」，反問過去是誰向金管局提出道具鈔票的申請。他強調，即使只有一張流失、混在真鈔中亦難免有人會受騙，可被不法之徒所用且造成社會損失，並以道具槍作例，稱有人會使用道具槍搶劫銀行，故非屬小事。<br />\n<br />\n他形容，本港法例表明不可複製可被誤認為真鈔的物件，只要不會複製出一件可被使用及誤認的道具鈔票，例如字樣、顏色或大小不同，均不會墮入法網，但今次案件中「道具」的字眼不突出，有機會被誤認為真鈔。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，現今科技先進，業界拍攝電影時可以「電子製作」方式取代使用實物，「你睇大場面Star War星球大戰，拍得好真實㗎」。另外，他指若在完成拍攝後銷毀道具鈔票，亦不會發生今次事件。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180531/large/1527778381_187d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180531%2Flarge%2F1527778381_187d.png&h=1c0ebeec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"10ee4549afaf24adf95fa034502013b180c0965a","tid":687236,"uid":42967,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T05:35:05.000Z","msg":"衰十一大哂？"},{"pid":"24aa9555e68d4c3a61c0206cb5ab5d6011c4eac8","tid":687236,"uid":41500,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T05:36:56.000Z","msg":"親政府就大哂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n公開地方煽動殺人,只要佢親政府就大哂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b590bd414bde782b9cba72b98a24b350ba537c7","tid":687236,"uid":990,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T05:37:53.000Z","msg":"11哥自已做就得"},{"pid":"ae2d3ab51e1c93212d3dcca73d4cb0ab8dd22bee","tid":687236,"uid":134323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T05:38:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"></span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>淚</strong></span>"},{"pid":"5d0ce0136533a2d934b82c10e1238c81df35ffcd","tid":687236,"uid":60333,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T05:43:52.000Z","msg":"係囉<br />\n犯左法淚灑雪廠街喎<br />\n仲唔撚去自首架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dee5509b5ddf613667ab65c8f937eebfd71f933","tid":687236,"uid":139700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T05:45:57.000Z","msg":"死仆街，佢徒弟羊惡橋呢?"},{"pid":"a25a4c037a23850d804f3c00c2c427a77e10f018","tid":687236,"uid":78971,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T05:46:23.000Z","msg":"湯渣做咩狙擊得咁撚落力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f5a481e098be5a4182b180bc1edcc84f01ecb3e","tid":687236,"uid":80814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T05:47:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/02/134605_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F02%2F134605_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=5b57b380&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都奇怪點解湯渣會咁肉緊呢單案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aa8fe5b5e54afbebcce0679654f6bf592ec8ef2","tid":687236,"uid":80814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f5a481e098be5a4182b180bc1edcc84f01ecb3e","tid":687236,"uid":80814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T05:47:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/02/13460